headline: Tariffs could add $500M to offshore wind project cost, says Dominion CEO
summary: Dominion Energy estimates that by the end of Q2, the cost of its 2.6 GW Coastal Virginia Offshore Wind project will increase by at least $120 million due to new tariffs.
